9 \uc548\uc5d0 \ubaa8\ub4e0 \uac83\uc774 \ub2e8\uc11c\uac00 \ub41c\ub2e4.\n\uc2dc\uac04 \ub0b4\uc5d0 \ud0c8\ucd9c\ud558\uc9c0 \ubabb\ud558\uba74 \ub2eb\ud600\ubc84\ub9b0 \uc544\uc774\uc758 \ub9c8\uc74c\ucc98\ub7fc\n\uc774 \ubc29\ub3c4 \uc2a4\uc2a4\ub85c \uad73\uac8c \uc7a0\uaca8\ubc84\ub824 \ub354\uc774\uc0c1 \uc5f4\ub9ac\uc9c0 \uc54a\ub294\ub2e4.\n\n-\uadc0\ud558\uc758 \uc758\uacac\uc744 \uae30\ub2e4\ub9ac\uaca0\uc2b5\ub2c8\ub2e4.\n\ub354 \ub9ce\uc740 \uc5d0\ud53c\uc18c\ub4dc\ub4e4\uc774 \uc5ec\ub7ec\ubd84\uc744 \ucc3e\uc544\uac08 \uac83\uc785\ub2c8\ub2e4.", "short_description": "\uacf5\ud3ec \ubc29\ud0c8\ucd9cVR \uac8c\uc784 (\uc815\uc2dd\ubc84\uc804\uc744 \uc704\ud55c \ud2f0\uc800)\n-\ud63c\uc790\uc11c \ud50c\ub808\uc774 \ud558\uac70\ub098 \uce5c\uad6c\ub97c \ucd08\ub300\ud558\uc5ec \uc990\uae38 \uc218 \uc788\uc2b5\ub2c8\ub2e4"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Portrait.png", "id": "3403127939936935", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974527_3403127943270268_5982631016592496092_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=SaIOBl_kLHIQ7kNvgG-dSop&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AFumJmvRx2_9-L6WPWUHnNr&oh=00_AYAOuGd0peRbMuDvfmKisKWbcZyW-r9PsAisyHIB_DQa4Q&oe=66E42E78"}, {"file_name": "Landscape.png", "id": "927076248559542", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974773_927076251892875_8940624378489886719_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=a_JdqWW-BwsQ7kNvgHm-F49&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AFumJmvRx2_9-L6WPWUHnNr&oh=00_AYCU1PNuNOzMxi9ilSx7m91xzotsS5LvwhNP6c5N9tJMsw&oe=66E439DF"}, {"file_name": "Icon.png", "id": "790868906088752", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974859_790868909422085_8366478809179753009_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=84kmUkjaoyoQ7kNvgHir_Bj&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=AFumJmvRx2_9-L6WPWUHnNr&oh=00_AYDale2eVDYtvr8dj